OL,3,CSenior whistleblowers allege animal
OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,FFormer senior staff at Zoo allege that
OL,7,Fanimals are not being cared for
OL,8,Fproperly and workers are being bullied
OL,9,Fas part of a "toxic workplace" culture.
OL,11,FPictures obtained exclusively by ITV
OL,12,FNews show a female aardvark with
OL,13,Fsevere scratches down her back and
OL,14,Fsides after staff allegedly introduced
OL,15,Fher to a male too soon and did not
OL,16,Fmonitor them correctly.
