OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,FA sloth is seen lying on a hard floor
OL,7,Fat the bottom of a metal set of stairs
OL,8,Fwith other photos showing it in the
OL,9,Fcorner of stairs, on its back, and
OL,10,Fhugging a concrete pillar.
OL,12,FIt is also claimed goats have foot rot
OL,13,Fdue to the poor conditions they were
OL,14,Fkept in.
OL,16,FFollowing a year of investigation by
OL,17,FITV News reporter Katya Fowler and
OL,18,Fproducer Sophie Dulson, three
OL,19,Fprominent former zoo employees have
OL,20,Fchosen to speak out .
