OL,3,CSenior whistleblowers allege animal
OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,FQuentin Bloxham dedicated more than 40
OL,7,Fyears to Jersey Zoo, working closely
OL,8,Fwith founder Gerald Durrell; from the
OL,9,Fcharity's creation to it becoming a
OL,10,Fworld-leading conservation group for
OL,11,Fendangered animals.
OL,13,FHe recently visited and was shocked by
OL,14,Fwhat he saw, explaining: "I found the
OL,15,Faardvarks and sloths in particular
OL,16,Fwere kept in levels of accommodation
OL,17,Fwell short of what I would have
OL,18,Fexpected to see at Durrell."
