OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,FQuentin says aardvarks which are
OL,7,Fnocturnal, large creatures were kept
OL,8,Fin "too small" an enclosure and under
OL,9,F"glaring white lights" in the daytime.
OL,11,FDominic Wormell was Head of Mammals at
OL,12,FJersey Zoo for 34 years but .
OL,14,FHe tells ITV News: "I felt I couldn't
OL,15,Ffulfil my dreams and passions anymore
OL,16,Fso I had to leave.
