OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,F"We were encouraged to be champions,
OL,7,F'if you come and you're lucky enough
OL,8,Fto work at Jersey Zoo you're going to
OL,9,Fbe a champion for a species' ... that
OL,10,Ffeeling and that passion, certainly
OL,11,Fover the last few years, dissipated a
OL,12,Fbit and we've got a bit 'zoo-ey' for
OL,13,Fwant of a better word."
