OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,FCommenting on how the animals are now
OL,7,Flooked after at the zoo, Dominic adds:
OL,8,F"One would have to ask yourself, if
OL,9,Fyou went to the zoo today as a
OL,10,Fvisitor, is the area where the sloth
OL,11,Fis kept in the stairwell ... is that
OL,12,Fappropriate for a sensitive exotic
OL,13,Fmammal?
OL,15,F"I think people can make their own
OL,16,Fminds up on that."
OL,18,FThe zoo declined ITV News's request
OL,19,Ffor an immediate interview but has
OL,20,Foffered one next week with Interim
OL,21,FChief Executive Officer Becky Brewer.
