OL,6,FIn a statement, Chair Matthew
OL,7,FHatchwell says: "Regarding allegations
OL,8,Fabout staff behaviour, we cannot
OL,9,Fcomment on these matters publicly and
OL,10,Fhave a duty of care to all employees.
OL,12,F"We have been communicating with a
OL,13,Fnumber of individuals over the last 12
OL,14,Fmonths regarding concerns they have
OL,15,Fraised. We have addressed each concern
OL,16,Fdirectly with them, including an in-
OL,17,Fperson mediation.
