OL,3,CSenior whistleblowers allege animal
OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,F"We take allegations about poor animal
OL,7,Fwelfare incredibly seriously. In
OL,8,FSeptember 2023, we asked Jersey's
OL,9,FChief Veterinary Officer to undertake
OL,10,Fan inspection into the matters raised
OL,11,Faround the sloths and aardvarks, and
OL,12,Fshe found no concerns.
OL,14,F"We have done everything we can to
OL,15,Faddress concerns and will continue to
OL,16,Fimprove how we communicate with our
OL,17,Fstaff and provide opportunities for
OL,18,Ffeedback.
